Inline CSS

INSTRUCTIONS: Add inline CSS to this paragraph to make the text red.

<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Inline CSS</title>
    </head>
    <body>
    	<p>Hello World</p>
    </body>
</html>


Answer:
<!doctype html>
<html>
	<head>
    	<title>Inline CSS</title>
    </head>
    <body>
    	<p style="color:red;">Hello World</p>
    </body>
</html>